    "instructions": [
        "Set Instant Pot to Saute mode. Heat ghee and oil. Add hing, ginger, garlic, chili, and cashews. Cook for 1 minute.",
        "Add chopped onion and cook for 2 minutes until soft. Add chopped tomato and cook for 1 more minute.",
        "Add the chopped spinach and mustard greens. Cook until wilted (3-4 minutes).",
        "Add coriander powder, turmeric, red chili powder, and salt. Stir well.",
        "Add 1/2 cup water. Close lid and pressure cook on High for 10 minutes. Natural pressure release.",
        "Open lid. Use an immersion blender to puree the saag to your desired consistency (coarse or smooth).",
        "Set Instant Pot back to Saute mode. Add paneer cubes and simmer for 2-3 minutes.",
        "Stir in garam masala and heavy cream (if using). Serve hot with naan or rice."
